{
  "category": "state",
  "title": "State attributes",
  "description": {
    "en": "State attributes control visibility, interaction, and opacity. Most are Boolean; `visibility` is tri-state.",
    "ja": "状態属性は可視性、インタラクション、不透明度を制御する。ほとんどが Boolean、`visibility` のみ三値。"
  },
  "kicker": "Attribute category · Reference",
  "kickerParentLabel": "Attributes",
